{{!}} Am I forced to use the new {{project name long}} Linux Installer?
{{!}} No, the previous way of installing manually VirtualBox and importing {{project name long}} into VirtualBox when following the [[VirtualBox{{!}}{{project name long}} for VirtualBox]] wiki page is still supported.
{{!}}-

{{!}} Will the manual VirtualBox installation method be deprecated in the future?
{{!}} Not planned at time of writing. Deprecation of the manual installation method is also unlikely for now because these instructions these provide compatibility with Linux distributions which {{project name long}} Linux Installer does not support.
{{!}}-

{{!}} Can I combine {{project_name_gateway_long}} CLI with {{project_name_workstation_long}} Xfce?
